OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784573305
OL,3,CMurderer and kidnapper Michael Sams
OL,4,Creferred to parole board
OL,6,FMichael Sams, who kidnapped and killed
OL,7,FJulie Dart and abducted Stephanie
OL,8,FSlater has been referred to the Parole
OL,9,FBoard.
OL,11,FSams, originally from Keighley in West
OL,12,FYorkshire, was given four life
OL,13,Fsentences in 1993 for the kidnap and
OL,14,Fmurder of Miss Dart and the kidnap of
OL,15,FBirmimgham estate agent Stephanie
OL,16,FSlater.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
