OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784573305
OL,3,CMurderer and kidnapper Michael Sams
OL,4,Creferred to parole board
OL,6,FIn a statement a parole board
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "We can confirm the
OL,8,Fparole review of Michael Sams has been
OL,9,Freferred to the Parole Board by the
OL,10,FSecretary of State for Justice and is
OL,11,Ffollowing standard processes."
OL,13,FThe 84-year-old has had several
OL,14,Funsuccessful parole reviews during his
OL,15,F33 years spent in prison.
OL,17,FEighteen-year-old Julie Dart was
OL,18,Fkidnapped by Sams in Leeds in 1991
OL,19,Fbefore being murdered and dumped on
OL,20,Ffarmland near Grantham, Lincolnshire.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784573305
OL,3,CMurderer and kidnapper Michael Sams
OL,4,Creferred to parole board
OL,6,FShe had been held prisoner by Sams in
OL,7,Fa coffin-like box in his workshop in
OL,8,FNewark, Nottinghamshire.
OL,10,FDespite demanding a #140,000 ransom
OL,11,Ffrom her family, Sams murdered her
OL,12,Fwith a hammer before disposing of her
OL,13,Fbody.
OL,15,FIt was during a later taped confession
OL,16,Fat Full Sutton Prison in East
OL,17,FYorkshire that Sams revealed it was
OL,18,Falways his intention to kill her.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784573305
OL,3,CMurderer and kidnapper Michael Sams
OL,4,Creferred to parole board
OL,6,FMonths later he kidnapped 25-year-old
OL,7,Festate agent Stephanie Slater from
OL,8,FGreat Barr in Birmingham, and took her
OL,9,Fto the same hide-out where he kept
OL,10,FJulie Dart.
OL,12,FFor eight days she was kept
OL,13,Fhandcuffed, gagged and blindfolded
OL,14,Finside a similar coffin-like box,
OL,15,Fwhich was inside a locked wheelie bin
OL,16,Flaid on its side. She was later found
OL,17,Falive.
OL,19,FSams admitted the kidnap of Miss
OL,20,FSlater, but denied Miss Dart's murder.
OL,21,FHe was convicted after a trial.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784573305
OL,3,CMurderer and kidnapper Michael Sams
OL,4,Creferred to parole board
OL,6,FStephanie Slater died in 2017 from
OL,7,Fcancer after she dedicated her life to
OL,8,Fhelping kidnap victims by working with
OL,9,Fpolice forces across the country.
OL,11,FA Parole Board spokesperson said:
OL,12,F"Parole Board decisions are solely
OL,13,Ffocused on what risk a prisoner could
OL,14,Frepresent to the public if released
OL,15,Fand whether that risk is manageable in
OL,16,Fthe community.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784573305
OL,3,CMurderer and kidnapper Michael Sams
OL,4,Creferred to parole board
OL,6,F"A panel will carefully examine a huge
OL,7,Frange of evidence, including details
OL,8,Fof the original crime, and any
OL,9,Fevidence of behaviour change, as well
OL,10,Fas explore the harm done and impact
OL,11,Fthe crime has had on the victims.
OL,13,F"Members read and digest hundreds of
OL,14,Fpages of evidence and reports in the
OL,15,Flead up to an oral hearing.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784573305
OL,3,CMurderer and kidnapper Michael Sams
OL,4,Creferred to parole board
OL,6,F"Evidence from witnesses such as
OL,7,Fprobation officers, psychiatrists and
OL,8,Fpsychologists, officials supervising
OL,9,Fthe offender in prison as well as
OL,10,Fvictim personal statements may be
OL,11,Fgiven at the hearing.
OL,13,F"It is standard for the prisoner and
OL,14,Fwitnesses to be questioned at length
OL,15,Fduring the hearing which often lasts a
OL,16,Ffull day or more. Parole reviews are
OL,17,Falways undertaken thoroughly and with
OL,18,Fextreme care. Protecting the public is
OL,19,Four number one priority."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
